SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year  =  1997 AND ci.person_id  >  2788278 AND ci.role_id  >  1
